collectionMetadata.name: Exports of Energy Products
collectionMetadata.description: Shows annual total energy exports by energy products (in ktoe)

datasetMetadata.name: Exports of Energy Products, 2005 to 2020
datasetMetadata.description:
Notes:
a. Numbers may not add up to the totals due to rounding.
b. All data are compiled from Enterprise Singapore's trade statistics.
c. Enterprise Singapore releases trade data in mass units. EMA releases similar data in energy units (ktoe).
d. The product classification of energy products differs from that used by Enterprise Singapore for trade statistics. 

Notations:
 - nil, negligible or not applicable
